snippet.title: PlayStation Experience 2015: Rez Infinite - Live Debut | PS VR
snippet.description:
The world's first glimpse at Rez Infinite -- the ultimate version of Sega's classic psychodelic rail-shooter adventure Rez, fully remastered and evolved, including VR support and additional new content, all by members of the original development team. 

http://enhancegames.com/

©Enhance Games, Inc. ©SEGA
